<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="ideefc1f65-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1978—<ref href="/us/pl/95/501">Pub. L. 95–501</ref> substituted “this subchapter” for “this chapter”.</p>
